                      },
                      "date": 1978
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "#doi:10.1016/0370-2693(78)90052-7"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "1USABRK",
                "1USAORU"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1USABRK"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The super heavy ion linear accelerator",
                " (SuperHILAC)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The lower-energy bombardment lasted 60 minutes with",
                "an average intensity of 9.3x10**13 particles/minute,",
                "while the higher-energy bombardment lasted for 108",
                "minutes with an average intensity of 4.7x10**13",
                "particles/ minute."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Ge(Li) gamma-ray spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Isotopically pure 208Pb targets of thickness 42-45",
                "mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 208Pb targets were irradiated with beams of",
                "48Ca ions of incident energy 300 and 410 MeV from the",
                "SuperHILAC of the Lawrence Berkeley Laboratory.",
                "Absolute cross sections were measured only in the",
                "higher-energy bombardment due to difficulties in",
                "determining the number of 48Ca ions passing through",
                "the target in the lower-energy irradiation. Following",
                "the bombardments the induced radioactivities in the",
                "target were detected with a gamma-ray spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The decay of the observed activities was",
                "followed for a period of approximately two months.",
                "Specific radionuclides produced were identified on",
                "the basis of gamma-ray energy, half-life and relative",
                "abundance of associated gamma-rays. In this manner 94",
                "and 109 radionuclides were identified in the low- and",
                "high-energy reactions, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
